{"tid":2163249,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"像極了愛情 - 林夕","createTime":"2020-08-18T14:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T21:53:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"016e9e203c554b50d00bc9ef9b727e9ee4c58128","tid":2163249,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:15:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/JHBI54PK55C5PHA36HFMTL73ZA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FJHBI54PK55C5PHA36HFMTL73ZA%2F&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5kHQxt1T4ELL4DwIHxiqIsg%3D&h=e8fa12fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FJHBI54PK55C5PHA36HFMTL73ZA%2F&h=32df0216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/JHBI54PK55C5PHA36HFMTL73ZA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n像極了愛情 - 林夕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WkOJHkbN0nlMlRdkBE8jZglGIzs=/1920x1397/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FY7QAUHVTRAU5GBB4DDGK5VQHA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWkOJHkbN0nlMlRdkBE8jZglGIzs%3D%2F1920x1397%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFY7QAUHVTRAU5GBB4DDGK5VQHA.jpg&h=6974abc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高雄市長補選前，陳其邁形容在高雄一路走來「像極了愛情」，對手李眉蓁諷刺也自表：「那高雄就是我唯一的初戀」。<br />\n<br />\n對一個地方的感情，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n特首臉書寫了篇七百字表白書，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n果然翻臉快過翻篇，比愛情小說更離奇，對方如今覺得特首沒有像個特首的樣，「像極了愛情」，當初看中你，是沒發覺你品行有點點兒疑惑，問了一下，再請你交代以下有沒有家暴，你，是心虛，還是怎麼的，先提出分手一方就贏了？手上那樽鹽，其實即是變核酸，酸爆。<br />\n<br />\n話說愛情關係，分手不是一場比賽，先開口就考第一。是哪一方不滿意對方，你知我知身邊人知，不發一言先放手，是放得下；對方沒拿定主意，長篇大論留下分手自白書，像極了分手男女自拍了很長很長的影片，長度與重視戀人名銜成比。<br />\n<br />\n黃秋生說這像極了港女，雖然也只是比喻，我為港女不值也。今日港女不似過去，尊嚴度偏高，機敏又狠辣，早早預感到不對勁，就第一時間甩了對方。<br />\n<br />\n特首自白書提到：「。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n以上都只以特首之名，因為是人家也是因特首之名而給她名譽。<br />\n<br />\n用回實名制，林鄭對所謂制裁、所謂虛名，都一笑置之，不屑一顧，不稀罕踏足美國，英國劍橋名譽銜頭又從不看重，這才猛然發現，原來她是個無求無慾，只追求權力，哪怕是虛位，也堅決違反諾言，你不撇我，我誓死不會分手。"},{"pid":"eccbc47f4e90fad5363ed5cbac6641fedee45d1a","tid":2163249,"uid":185669,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:29:03.000Z","msg":"仆你個街 入嚟睇林夕屌你變咗睇林鄭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c1b8ebe07b68a154cd610bcebbf4554ed250b9","tid":2163249,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:30:31.000Z","msg":"林夕定林鄭? <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0ada9f18eab1d29e103216379afe69760305c5","tid":2163249,"uid":312513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eccbc47f4e90fad5363ed5cbac6641fedee45d1a","tid":2163249,"uid":185669,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:29:03.000Z","msg":"仆你個街 入嚟睇林夕屌你變咗睇林鄭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T21:52:46.000Z","msg":"個專欄作家咪係夕爺囉"},{"pid":"b794b77b57affd7ba933336ab979590d751afe5d","tid":2163249,"uid":312513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8c1b8ebe07b68a154cd610bcebbf4554ed250b9","tid":2163249,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:30:31.000Z","msg":"林夕定林鄭? <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T21:53:07.000Z","msg":"why not both"}]}